## 1.4 System Overview

The {{product}} is a cloud-native, microservices-based platform that provides:

- **RESTful API Gateway**: Single entry point for all client requests
- **Authentication Service**: OAuth 2.0 based authentication and authorization
- **Core Services**: Domain-specific microservices for business logic
- **Data Layer**: Distributed database architecture with caching
- **Analytics Pipeline**: Real-time and batch analytics processing

<<mermaid>>
  graph TB
    A[Client Applications] --> B[Load Balancer]
    B --> C[API Gateway]
    C --> D{Authentication}
    D -->|Valid| E[Service Mesh]
    D -->|Invalid| F[401 Unauthorized]
    E --> G[Auth Service]
    E --> H[User Service]
    E --> I[Data Service]
    E --> J[Analytics Service]
    G --> K[(Auth DB)]
    H --> L[(User DB)]
    I --> M[(Main DB)]
    J --> N[(Analytics DB)]
    E --> O[Cache Layer]
    O --> P[Redis Cluster]
    
    style C fill:#4285F4,color:#fff
    style D fill:#FBBC04,color:#000
    style E fill:#34A853,color:#fff
    style F fill:#EA4335,color:#fff

*Figure 1: High-level system architecture overview*

